===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], Sexton had 46 residents, 19 households, and 12 families.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A71715&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 2, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A71715&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 2, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The median age was 28.5 years. 21.7% of residents were under the age of 18, and 17.4% were 65 years of age or older. The age distribution was 21.7% under age 20, 13.0% from 20 to 24, 30.4% from 25 to 44, 17.4% from 45 to 64, and 17.4% age 65 or older. The gender makeup of the community was 50.0% male and 50.0% female. For every 100 females there were 100.0 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 89.5 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A71715&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 2, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> Of the 19 households, 26.3% had children under age 18 living with them, 63.2% were married-couple households, 5.3% were cohabiting-couple households, 31.6% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present, and 0.0% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present. About 36.8% of households were non-families, 31.6% were made up of individuals, and 26.3% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

There were 19 housing units, with 0.0% vacant housing units. The [[population density]] was 20.9 inhabitants per square mile (8.1/km<sup>2</sup>), and the housing-unit density was 8.6 per square mile (3.3/km<sup>2</sup>). The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

